{"video_id": "rgFgDCnVDM0", "title": "063  Srila Prabhupada is the Summum bonum of all acharyas", "speaker": "HDG Srila Prabhupada", "youtube_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rgFgDCnVDM0", "duration": 229, "segments": [{"start": 0.0, "end": 7.0, "text": " What is the essence of all Shastra?"}, {"start": 7.0, "end": 11.0, "text": " The Prophet has taught the essence of all Shastra."}, {"start": 11.0, "end": 13.0, "text": " One time we went to Sri Rangam."}, {"start": 13.0, "end": 14.0, "text": " There used to be..."}, {"start": 14.0, "end": 16.0, "text": " Actually, when we first came to Sri Rangam,"}, {"start": 16.0, "end": 17.0, "text": " there was..."}, {"start": 17.0, "end": 18.0, "text": " They had a sign there,"}, {"start": 18.0, "end": 19.0, "text": " Non-Hindus Allowed."}, {"start": 19.0, "end": 21.0, "text": " There was one life member in Shishadipuram."}, {"start": 21.0, "end": 23.0, "text": " He sent his car with us."}, {"start": 23.0, "end": 24.0, "text": " So we went to Sri Rangam,"}, {"start": 24.0, "end": 27.0, "text": " and we did not know we were Westerners."}, {"start": 27.0, "end": 28.0, "text": " So we tried to go over to Darshanam."}, {"start": 28.0, "end": 29.0, "text": " He says,"}, {"start": 29.0, "end": 30.0, "text": " No, Non-Hindus Allowed."}, {"start": 30.0, "end": 31.0, "text": " You are Mleches."}, {"start": 31.0, "end": 32.0, "text": " You cannot go."}, {"start": 32.0, "end": 33.0, "text": " The only person who can let you in"}, {"start": 33.0, "end": 35.0, "text": " is this Archaka."}, {"start": 35.0, "end": 36.0, "text": " This Rangaraj Bhatta."}, {"start": 36.0, "end": 38.0, "text": " Rangaraj Bhatta at that time"}, {"start": 38.0, "end": 41.0, "text": " was the chief Archaka of the Sri Rangam temple."}, {"start": 41.0, "end": 43.0, "text": " So where does he live?"}, {"start": 43.0, "end": 44.0, "text": " Since we went there."}, {"start": 44.0, "end": 45.0, "text": " So we see this Brahmin."}, {"start": 45.0, "end": 46.0, "text": " Big, big Brahmin."}, {"start": 46.0, "end": 47.0, "text": " Oh, very big."}, {"start": 47.0, "end": 50.0, "text": " Must have been..."}, {"start": 50.0, "end": 52.0, "text": " Those of you who know a little Sanskrit,"}, {"start": 52.0, "end": 54.0, "text": " Vishnur Alankaram Priyam,"}, {"start": 54.0, "end": 56.0, "text": " Brahmanam Bhojanam Priyam."}, {"start": 56.0, "end": 57.0, "text": " You know?"}, {"start": 57.0, "end": 58.0, "text": " Yes."}, {"start": 58.0, "end": 59.0, "text": " He fulfilled that."}, {"start": 59.0, "end": 60.0, "text": " He sits there."}, {"start": 60.0, "end": 61.0, "text": " He comes out of his house."}, {"start": 61.0, "end": 62.0, "text": " He says,"}, {"start": 62.0, "end": 63.0, "text": " Oh, you have come."}, {"start": 63.0, "end": 64.0, "text": " We did not know him."}, {"start": 64.0, "end": 65.0, "text": " He says,"}, {"start": 65.0, "end": 66.0, "text": " He offered his obeisances."}, {"start": 66.0, "end": 67.0, "text": " He says,"}, {"start": 67.0, "end": 68.0, "text": " Come inside."}, {"start": 68.0, "end": 69.0, "text": " First thing we see inside,"}, {"start": 69.0, "end": 70.0, "text": " there's a picture of Chaitanya Mahaprabhu."}, {"start": 70.0, "end": 71.0, "text": " He says,"}, {"start": 71.0, "end": 72.0, "text": " What is this picture?"}, {"start": 72.0, "end": 74.0, "text": " Oh, we are descendants of Gopal Bhattagoswami."}, {"start": 74.0, "end": 75.0, "text": " Really?"}, {"start": 75.0, "end": 76.0, "text": " Oh, yeah."}, {"start": 76.0, "end": 77.0, "text": " He lived..."}, {"start": 77.0, "end": 78.0, "text": " Your Mahaprabhu came to this house."}, {"start": 78.0, "end": 79.0, "text": " Actually,"}, {"start": 79.0, "end": 80.0, "text": " when Chaitanya Mahaprabhu"}, {"start": 80.0, "end": 81.0, "text": " visited Sri Rangam"}, {"start": 81.0, "end": 82.0, "text": " in about 15,"}, {"start": 82.0, "end": 83.0, "text": " 14,"}, {"start": 83.0, "end": 84.0, "text": " something like that,"}, {"start": 84.0, "end": 85.0, "text": " he stayed in that house"}, {"start": 85.0, "end": 86.0, "text": " to observe Chaturmasya."}, {"start": 86.0, "end": 87.0, "text": " Very old house."}, {"start": 87.0, "end": 88.0, "text": " So they worshipped Mahaprabhu."}, {"start": 88.0, "end": 89.0, "text": " They worshipped Chaturmasya."}, {"start": 89.0, "end": 90.0, "text": " They worshipped Mahaprabhu"}, {"start": 90.0, "end": 91.0, "text": " on the wall."}, {"start": 91.0, "end": 92.0, "text": " They are descendants..."}, {"start": 92.0, "end": 93.0, "text": " They are direct descendants"}, {"start": 93.0, "end": 94.0, "text": " of the relatives of Gopal Bhattag."}, {"start": 94.0, "end": 95.0, "text": " And he told us..."}, {"start": 95.0, "end": 96.0, "text": " Then he says,"}, {"start": 96.0, "end": 97.0, "text": " I will show you another deity."}, {"start": 97.0, "end": 99.0, "text": " He took us to another little street there."}, {"start": 99.0, "end": 102.0, "text": " And they have very old Jagannath deities"}, {"start": 102.0, "end": 104.0, "text": " that Chaitanya Mahaprabhu worshipped"}, {"start": 104.0, "end": 105.0, "text": " when he was in Jagannath Puri."}, {"start": 105.0, "end": 106.0, "text": " So then he sat us down."}, {"start": 106.0, "end": 107.0, "text": " And he brought us to the temple."}, {"start": 107.0, "end": 108.0, "text": " And he,"}, {"start": 108.0, "end": 109.0, "text": " of course,"}, {"start": 109.0, "end": 110.0, "text": " he spoke very good Tamil."}, {"start": 110.0, "end": 111.0, "text": " And he chastised them,"}, {"start": 111.0, "end": 112.0, "text": " chastised the Brahmins."}, {"start": 112.0, "end": 113.0, "text": " No, no,"}, {"start": 113.0, "end": 114.0, "text": " let them,"}, {"start": 114.0, "end": 115.0, "text": " let them."}, {"start": 115.0, "end": 116.0, "text": " Then he brought us."}, {"start": 116.0, "end": 117.0, "text": " And we had the darshan of Lord Ranganath"}, {"start": 117.0, "end": 118.0, "text": " and everything."}, {"start": 118.0, "end": 119.0, "text": " And we spent some time"}, {"start": 119.0, "end": 120.0, "text": " with them."}, {"start": 120.0, "end": 121.0, "text": " And we showed them"}, {"start": 121.0, "end": 122.0, "text": " one of Prabhupada's books."}, {"start": 122.0, "end": 123.0, "text": " At that time,"}, {"start": 123.0, "end": 124.0, "text": " we did not have the..."}, {"start": 124.0, "end": 126.0, "text": " This was 1972."}, {"start": 126.0, "end": 127.0, "text": " We did not have"}, {"start": 127.0, "end": 128.0, "text": " the whole,"}, {"start": 128.0, "end": 129.0, "text": " the whole Bhagavata."}, {"start": 129.0, "end": 130.32, "text": " We just had the first canto."}, {"start": 130.32, "end": 131.32, "text": " So he looked at this."}, {"start": 131.32, "end": 132.32, "text": " Of course,"}, {"start": 132.32, "end": 133.32, "text": " these,"}, {"start": 133.32, "end": 134.32, "text": " these pandits,"}, {"start": 134.32, "end": 135.32, "text": " they know Sanskrit very well."}, {"start": 135.32, "end": 136.32, "text": " And he's looking,"}, {"start": 136.32, "end": 137.32, "text": " he was looking at all the pictures."}, {"start": 137.32, "end": 138.32, "text": " He says,"}, {"start": 138.32, "end": 139.32, "text": " actually,"}, {"start": 139.32, "end": 140.32, "text": " I want to tell you something."}, {"start": 140.32, "end": 141.32, "text": " He says,"}, {"start": 141.32, "end": 142.32, "text": " your guru,"}, {"start": 142.32, "end": 143.32, "text": " he's the samambonam of all acharyas."}, {"start": 143.32, "end": 144.32, "text": " He says,"}, {"start": 144.32, "end": 148.76, "text": " how do you say that?"}, {"start": 148.76, "end": 148.88, "text": " And we asked him,"}, {"start": 148.88, "end": 149.88, "text": " how do you say that?"}, {"start": 149.88, "end": 150.88, "text": " He says,"}, {"start": 150.88, "end": 151.88, "text": " because in order to do this,"}, {"start": 151.88, "end": 152.88, "text": " you,"}, {"start": 152.88, "end": 153.88, "text": " not only do you have to know Sanskrit,"}, {"start": 153.88, "end": 154.88, "text": " but you have to know"}, {"start": 154.88, "end": 155.88, "text": " just not the Sanskrit."}, {"start": 155.88, "end": 156.88, "text": " You have to be able to read"}, {"start": 156.88, "end": 157.88, "text": " all the commentaries"}, {"start": 157.88, "end": 158.88, "text": " of the acharyas."}, {"start": 158.88, "end": 159.88, "text": " Just what we read today."}, {"start": 159.88, "end": 160.88, "text": " Actually,"}, {"start": 160.88, "end": 161.88, "text": " when Prabhupada was here"}, {"start": 161.88, "end": 162.88, "text": " a few times,"}, {"start": 162.88, "end": 163.88, "text": " we had the chance at night"}, {"start": 163.88, "end": 164.88, "text": " in 1977"}, {"start": 164.88, "end": 165.88, "text": " to watch Prabhupada"}, {"start": 165.88, "end": 166.88, "text": " translate the book."}, {"start": 166.88, "end": 167.88, "text": " And he had this big,"}, {"start": 167.88, "end": 168.88, "text": " big book."}, {"start": 168.88, "end": 169.88, "text": " It must have been like,"}, {"start": 169.88, "end": 170.88, "text": " it's a huge book"}, {"start": 170.88, "end": 171.88, "text": " that was published"}, {"start": 171.88, "end": 172.88, "text": " 200 years ago."}, {"start": 172.88, "end": 173.88, "text": " It has all the Sanskrit commentaries"}, {"start": 173.88, "end": 174.88, "text": " of all the Vaishnava acharyas."}, {"start": 174.88, "end": 175.88, "text": " It has the commentary"}, {"start": 175.88, "end": 176.88, "text": " of Vijaya Advaita."}, {"start": 176.88, "end": 177.88, "text": " It has the commentary"}, {"start": 177.88, "end": 178.64, "text": " of the Vedic scriptures."}, {"start": 178.64000000000001, "end": 179.64000000000001, "text": " It has the commentary"}, {"start": 179.64000000000001, "end": 180.64000000000001, "text": " of the Vedic literature."}, {"start": 180.64000000000001, "end": 181.64000000000001, "text": " It has the commentary"}, {"start": 181.64000000000001, "end": 182.64000000000001, "text": " of the Madhva Sampradaya."}, {"start": 182.64000000000001, "end": 183.64000000000001, "text": " It has the commentary"}, {"start": 183.64000000000001, "end": 184.64000000000001, "text": " of the Viragavacharya"}, {"start": 184.64000000000001, "end": 185.64000000000001, "text": " of the Sri Sampradaya."}, {"start": 185.64000000000001, "end": 186.64000000000001, "text": " It has the commentary"}, {"start": 186.64000000000001, "end": 187.64000000000001, "text": " of the Vala Bhacharyas."}, {"start": 187.64000000000001, "end": 188.64000000000001, "text": " It has the commentary"}, {"start": 188.64000000000001, "end": 189.64000000000001, "text": " of the Jiva Goswami."}, {"start": 189.64000000000001, "end": 190.64000000000001, "text": " It has the commentary"}, {"start": 190.64000000000001, "end": 191.64000000000001, "text": " of the Sanatana Goswami."}, {"start": 191.64000000000001, "end": 192.64000000000001, "text": " It has the commentary"}, {"start": 192.64000000000001, "end": 193.64000000000001, "text": " of the Prophet's Guru,"}, {"start": 193.64000000000001, "end": 194.64000000000001, "text": " Bhaktisiddhanta's commentary,"}, {"start": 194.64000000000001, "end": 195.64000000000001, "text": " Bhaktivinoda Thakur's commentary."}, {"start": 195.64000000000001, "end": 196.64000000000001, "text": " So many commentaries"}, {"start": 196.64000000000001, "end": 197.64000000000001, "text": " all in Sanskrit."}, {"start": 197.64000000000001, "end": 198.64000000000001, "text": " In order to produce these,"}, {"start": 198.64000000000001, "end": 199.64000000000001, "text": " you know,"}, {"start": 199.64000000000001, "end": 200.64000000000001, "text": " 25, 26 lines,"}, {"start": 200.64000000000001, "end": 201.64000000000001, "text": " the Prophet would sometimes"}, {"start": 201.64000000000001, "end": 202.64000000000001, "text": " take an hour"}, {"start": 202.64000000000001, "end": 203.64000000000001, "text": " and he's analyzing"}, {"start": 203.64000000000001, "end": 204.64000000000001, "text": " all of this."}, {"start": 204.64000000000001, "end": 205.64000000000001, "text": " And he's giving these purports."}, {"start": 205.64000000000001, "end": 206.64000000000001, "text": " So these purports"}, {"start": 206.64000000000001, "end": 207.64000000000001, "text": " of all the essence"}, {"start": 207.64000000000001, "end": 208.64000000000001, "text": " of all these Acharyas."}, {"start": 208.64000000000001, "end": 209.64000000000001, "text": " Another time,"}, {"start": 209.64000000000001, "end": 210.64000000000001, "text": " one devotee asked,"}, {"start": 210.64000000000001, "end": 211.64000000000001, "text": " O Prophet,"}, {"start": 211.64000000000001, "end": 212.64000000000001, "text": " why don't you translate faster?"}, {"start": 212.64000000000001, "end": 213.64000000000001, "text": " We want to publish more books"}, {"start": 213.64000000000001, "end": 214.64000000000001, "text": " quicker, quicker."}, {"start": 214.64000000000001, "end": 215.64000000000001, "text": " The Prophet says,"}, {"start": 215.64000000000001, "end": 216.64000000000001, "text": " you do not understand."}, {"start": 216.64000000000001, "end": 217.64000000000001, "text": " You do not understand."}, {"start": 217.64000000000001, "end": 218.64000000000001, "text": " He says,"}, {"start": 218.64000000000001, "end": 219.64000000000001, "text": " these books"}, {"start": 219.64000000000001, "end": 220.64000000000001, "text": " are my devotional ecstasies."}]}